beat protocol\"),\n    57→            (\"~/agni-workspace/RESOURCE_MAP.md\", \"Model routing, costs\"),\n    58→            (\"~/trishula/\", \"Inter-VPS messaging system (813 msgs in inbox)\"),\n    59→            (\"~/trishula/inbox/INBOX_TRIAGE_BRIEF_20260214.md\", \"Inbox triage: 7 tickets, security findings\"),\n    60→            (\"~/saraswati-dharmic-agora/\", \"Dharmic Agora repo (local clone)\"),\n    61→            (\"~/.chaiwala/message_bus.py\", \"CHAIWALA message bus (SQLite, 405 lines)\"),\n    62→        ],\n    63→    },\n    64→    \"identity\": {\n    65→        \"description\": \"Core identity, soul, vision documents\",\n    66→        \"paths\": [\n    67→            (\"~/agni-workspace/SOUL.md\", \"The recognition attractor. S(x)=x.\"),\n    68→            (\"~/agni-workspace/CONSTITUTION.md\", \"Immutable constraints\"),\n    69→            (\"~/agni-workspace/AGENTS.md\", \"Complete nervous system\"),\n    70→            (\"~/agni-workspace/NORTH_STAR/SAB_500_YEAR_VISION.md\", \"THE strategic document\"),\n    71→            (\"~/agni-workspace/STAR_MAP.md\", \"Power ranking of all files\"),\n    72→            (\"~/agni-workspace/NORTH_STAR/90_DAY_COUNTER_ATTRACTOR.md\", \"Urgency engine\"),\n    73→        ],\n    74→    },\n    75→    \"vault\": {\n    76→        \"description\": \"Obsidian vault, contemplative materials\",\n    77→        \"paths\": [\n    78→            (\"~/Desktop/KAILASH ABODE OF SHIVA/\", \"Obsidian vault -- 590+ files\"),\n    79→            (\"~/agni-workspace/knowledge/seeds/the-mother-for-ai-fire.md\", \"Crown jewel -- Aurobindo x AI\"),\n    80→            (\"~/agni-workspace/knowledge/evergreen/alignment-as-thermodynamics.md\", \"Potential Nature paper\"),\n    81→            (\"~/agni-workspace/knowledge/evergreen/triple-mapping.md\", \"2,500 year convergent validity\"),\n    82→        ],\n    83→    },\n    84→    \"jagat_kalyan\": {\n    85→        \"description\": \"Jagat Kalyan -- AI-coordinated ecological restoration\",\n    86→        \"paths\": [\n    87→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/\", \"JK project root -- FastAPI MVP\"),\n    88→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/app.py\", \"FastAPI application (17KB)\"),\n    89→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/matching.py\", \"Claude API + heuristic matching engine\"),\n    90→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/models.py\", \"SQLAlchemy models (Project, Funder, Match, Outcome)\"),\n    91→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/WELFARE_TONS_SPEC.md\", \"Mathematical spec: W = C*E*A*B*V*P (69KB)\"),\n    92→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/anthropic_grant_application.md\", \"$35K Anthropic Economic Futures grant app\"),\n    93→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/PARTNER_RESEARCH.md\", \"33 orgs across 6 categories\"),\n    94→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/CARBON_ATTRIBUTION_FEASIBILITY.md\", \"Per-inference carbon feasibility study\"),\n    95→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/SCOUT_LOG.md\", \"Autonomous intel gathering log\"),\n    96→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/EVOLUTION_LOG.md\", \"Codebase evolution history\"),\n    97→            (\"~/jagat_kalyan/pitches/\", \"3 pitch variants (one-pager, Anthropic, Substack)\"),\n    98→            (\"~/.dharma/shared/jk_pulse.md\", \"JK momentum heartbeat\"),\n    99→            (\"~/.dharma/shared/jk_alert.md\", \"HIGH URGENCY alerts for morning brief\"),\n   100→        ],\n   101→    },\n   102→    \"dgc\": {\n   103→        \"description\": \"DGC system itself\",\n   104→        \"paths\": [\n   105→            (\"~/dgc-core/\", \"THIS system -- Claude Code native DGC\"),\n   106→            (\"~/DHARMIC_GODEL_CLAW/\", \"Old DGC (75K lines, mostly dead)\"),\n   107→            (\"~/DHARMIC_GODEL_CLAW/src/core/telos_layer.py\", \"7 gates -- ported to hooks/\"),\n   108→            (\"~/DHARMIC_GODEL_CLAW/src/core/strange_memory.py\", \"Memory -- ported to memory/\"),\n   109→            (\"~/.claude/\", \"Claude Code config, agents, memory\"),\n   110→        ],\n   111→    },\n   112→}\n   113→\n   114→\n   115→def get_context_for(domain: str) -> str:\n   116→    \"\"\"Generate context string for a specific domain.\n   117→\n   118→    Args:\n   119→        domain: One of the ECOSYSTEM keys, or \"all\" for everything.\n   120→\n   121→    Returns:\n   122→        Formatted string with path existence checks and descriptions.\n   123→    \"\"\"\n   124→    if domain == \"all\":\n   125→        domains = list(ECOSYSTEM.keys())\n   126→    elif domain in ECOSYSTEM:\n   127→        domains = [domain]\n   128→    else:\n   129→        return f\"Unknown domain: {domain}. Available: {', '.join(ECOSYSTEM.keys())}\"\n   130→\n   131→    parts = [f\"# Dhyana's Filesystem -- {domain.upper()} Context\\n\"]\n   132→    parts.append(f\"Generated: {datetime.now().isoformat()[:19]}\\n\")\n   133→\n   134→    for d in domains:\n   135→        info = ECOSYSTEM[d]\n   136→        parts.append(f\"\\n## {d.upper()}: {info['description']}\")\n   137→        for path_str, desc in info[\"paths\"]:\n   138→            path = Path(path_str).expanduser()\n   139→            exists = path.exists()\n   140→            marker = \"OK\" if exists else \"MISSING\"\n   141→            parts.append(f\"  [{marker}] {path_str}\")\n   142→            parts.append(f\"         {desc}\")\n   143→\n   144→    return \"\\n\".join(parts)\n   145→\n   146→\n   147→def check_health() -> dict[str, int | dict[str, str]]:\n   148→    \"\"\"Check which ecosystem paths exist and which are missing.\n   149→\n   150→    Returns:\n   151→        Dict with 'ok' count, 'missing' count, and 'details' of missing paths.\n   152→    \"\"\"\n   153→    ok = 0\n   154→    missing = 0\n   155→    details: dict[str, str] = {}\n   156→    for _domain, info in ECOSYSTEM.items():\n   157→        for path_str, desc in info[\"paths\"]:\n   158→            path = Path(path_str).expanduser()\n   159→            if path.exists():\n   160→                ok += 1\n   161→            else:\n   162→                missing += 1\n   163→                details[path_str] = f\"MISSING -- {desc}\"\n   164→    return {\"ok\": ok, \"missing\": missing, \"details\": details}\n   165→\n   166→\n   167→if __name__ == \"__main__\":\n   168→    import sys\n   169→\n   170→    domain = sys.argv[1] if len(sys.argv) > 1 else \"all\"\n   171→\n   172→    if domain == \"health\":\n   173→        h = check_health()\n   174→        print(f\"Ecosystem: {h['ok']} OK, {h['missing']} MISSING\")\n   175→        details = h[\"details\"]\n   176→        assert isinstance(details, dict)\n   177→        for p, d in details.items():\n   178→            print(f\"  {d}: {p}\")\n   179→    else:\n   180→        print(get_context_for(domain))\n   181→"}]},"uuid":"13883d8d-9c93-4362-812b-63063d969977","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:19:55.136Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"7e7f6b84-add4-491a-8d38-e59e3a71284e","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
